	<h4 class="cs89687900">
		<span class="csB9803513">&sect;16-5U-1. Short title.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">[Repealed.]</span></p><h4 class="cs89687900">
		<span class="csB9803513">&sect;16-5U-2. Responsibilities of Bureau for Public Health.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">[Repealed.]</span></p><p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;</span></p><h4 class="cs89687900">
		<span class="csB9803513">&sect;16-5U-3. Interagency council on arthritis.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">[Repealed.]</span></p><h2 class="cs89687900">
