	<h2 class="cs89687900">
		<span class="csF5B7C975">ARTICLE 5BB. SCREENING PROTOCOLS FOR ADVERSE CHILDHOOD EXPERIENCES.</span></h2>
	<h4 class="cs89687900">
		<span class="csB9803513">&sect;16-5BB-1. Development of Screening Protocols for Adverse Childhood Experiences.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">[Repealed.]</span></p><h2 class="cs89687900">
